            * f4778ef Initial 1 on "Commit A"

        [O] #501 Commit B (gh/ezyang/2/head -> gh/ezyang/2/base)

            Stack:
            * __->__ #501
            * #500

            This is commit B

            * f33fe2b Rebase on "Commit B"
