        Repository state:

            *   51b1590 (gh/ezyang/1/head)
            |\\     Rebase on "Commit A"
            | * 0c51c0c (gh/ezyang/1/base)
            | |    Update base for Rebase on "Commit A"
            * | f4778ef
            |/     Initial 1 on "Commit A"
            * 6b23cb6
                 Update base for Initial 1 on "Commit A"
            *   f33fe2b (gh/ezyang/2/head)
            |\\     Rebase on "Commit B"
            | * 96db6fb (gh/ezyang/2/base)
